Yingwe yi le ka ntlawa lowu fanaka (Genus Panthera) na wa tinghala, na tilephadi na tijagwa. Swimanga leswi swa mune hi swona ntsena leswi kotaka ku vomba.
Ku vomba ka yingwe a ku fani na ku vomba loku heleleke ka nghala, kambe ku fana na xivulwa xa munhu loyi a kwateke loko a huwelela.
